A look at life for the 650,00 children living on the streets in Bangladesh. Also, The hotel workers in Argentina who took over the hotel when it went bankrupt. Criticism of the 'Da Vinci Code' film for its portrayal of Albinism. The benefit of a university education.The work of the Citizens Protection Committee in Delhi in handling religious tension in India. Show less